{"type":null,"faqId":33944,"title":"为什么不能唤醒手机？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">如下小窍门可以提高您唤醒手机的成功几率：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1）推荐您使用“标准唤醒词”，如果使用“自定义唤醒词” 建议使用4～5个音节，比较抑扬顿挫的词。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2）请尽量在安静的环境下进行唤醒词训练，并尽量使用日常生活中最自然的语速、语调进行训练。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3）太嘈杂的环境对手机的唤醒率和识别率都有影响</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8646","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748769000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":20,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"语音唤醒,失败","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}